Number of Loans/Properties:  63/141
Top-10 Concentration: 54.3 percent
Property Types: Retail (29.5 percent of pool balance), multifamily (19.4 percent), hotels (19.3 percent), office (18.7 percent), manufactured housing community (5.5 percent), industrial (4.6 percent), self storage (2.5 percent), mixed use (0.5 percent)
Underwritten DSCR: 2.04x
Underwritten LTV: 62.3 percent
Underwritten Debt Yield: 11.7 percent
Weighted Average Mortgage Rate: 4.514 percent
Subordinate Debt: 4 loans (18.6 percent of pool balance)
